OL,6,FAndrew Talbot, 54, "stuffed as much
OL,7,F(of the drug) as he could fit into his
OL,8,Fpockets" after visiting the secure
OL,9,Fstore more than 30 times, before then
OL,10,Fusing police computer systems to
OL,11,Fsearch for known dealers to help him
OL,12,Fsell it on.
OL,14,FThe former detective constable with
OL,15,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) was
OL,16,Fonly caught when he accidentally
OL,17,Fdropped a wrap of cocaine outside his
OL,18,Fdaughter's primary school in February
