OL,6,FJailing him at Liverpool Crown Court
OL,7,FJudge Neil Flewitt KC said: "As a
OL,8,Fresult of conscientious and dedicated
OL,9,Fpolice work, large quantities of Class
OL,10,FA drugs were taken off the streets by
OL,11,Fofficers of Greater Manchester Police,
OL,12,Fmany of whom were your colleagues.
OL,14,F"As a result of your addiction and
OL,15,Fgreed a significant quantity of that
OL,16,Fcocaine was put back into circulation.
OL,18,F"You deceived your colleagues and you
OL,19,Fbetrayed the trust placed in you by
OL,20,Fthem and the community."
