OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Jennifer
OL,7,FAdams, of GMP's Anti-Corruption Unit,
OL,8,Fsaid: "This is one of the most
OL,9,Fshocking cases of corruption we've
OL,10,Funcovered, and Talbot will now serve a
OL,11,Flong sentence behind bars for abusing
OL,12,Fhis role as a police officer.
OL,14,F"He betrayed his oath to serve the
OL,15,Fpublic and instead became a criminal;
OL,16,Fhe not only stole drugs that had been
OL,17,Ftaken from the streets, but he also
OL,18,Funlawfully used police systems and
OL,19,Fconspired with a known local drug
OL,20,Fdealer to add further crime and fear
OL,21,Fto communities.
